{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "# Rule Recommendations for Network Security Perimeter (NSP)\r\n\r\nThis dashboard provides access rule recommendations based on observed traffic patterns for resources within the Network Security Perimeter (NSP). These recommendations help administrators review and implement the required rules to support a smooth transition from learning mode to enforced mode.\r\n## Recommendations are generated for\r\n\r\n- **Microsoft inbound traffic** using Service Tag-based or IP-based rules. Service Tags are recommended for traffic originating from Azure services and Microsoft-managed infrastructure, while IP-based rules may be when more granular control is required.\r\n\r\n- **Non-Microsoft inbound traffic** using IP-based rules. These recommendations are derived from observed connections originating from external public IP addresses\r\n\r\n- **Outbound traffic** using FQDN-based rules derived from observed destination patterns. These recommendations help allow required outbound connectivity to services while avoiding overly permissive access controls.\r\n\r\n- **Denied traffic visibility** within the perimeter boundary, where traffic denied by resources or under NSP enforced mode is aggregated at the NSP level.\r\n\r\nUse these recommendations as a starting point to validate and configure NSP access rules, helping ensure legitimate traffic remains permitted when enforcement is enabled."
      },
      "name": "text - 8"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "Inputs Required",
        "expandable": true,
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "- **Time Range** – Select the period over which network traffic should be analyzed.\r\n- **Workspace Subscription** – Choose the subscription that contains the Log Analytics workspace.\r\n- **Log Analytics Workspace** – Select the workspace where Traffic Analytics data for your Network Security Perimeter (NSP) is collected.\r\n- **Network Security Perimeter (NSP)** – Select one or more NSPs for which you would like to view access rule recommendations."
            },
            "name": "supported services"
          }
        ]
      },
      "name": "workbook_services_support"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{workspace}"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "f79d5185-6941-488e-a728-3beaec49f9d4",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "timeInterval",
            "label": "Time Interval",
            "type": 4,
            "description": "Select time interval to get data",
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": {
              "durationMs": 1209600000
            },
            "typeSettings": {
              "selectableValues": [
                {
                  "durationMs": 1800000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 3600000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 43200000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 86400000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 604800000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 1209600000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 2592000000
                }
              ],
              "allowCustom": true
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "759afd4c-a6d6-4787-a033-8d6ac1f60a71",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "workspaceSubscription",
            "label": "LA workspace Subscription",
            "type": 5,
            "description": "Subscritpion where the Log Analytics workspace is present",
            "multiSelect": true,
            "quote": "'",
            "delimiter": ",",
            "query": "    resourcecontainers\r\n    | where type == 'microsoft.resources/subscriptions'\r\n    | project subscriptionId = id, subscriptionName = name",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "value::all"
            ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [
                "value::1"
              ],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "timeContext": {
              "durationMs": 86400000
            },
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
          },
          {
            "id": "0607187b-6749-4302-8d14-572e34e30061",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "workspace",
            "label": "Log Analytics Workspace",
            "type": 5,
            "description": "Log Analytics workspace with TA data",
            "query": "resources\r\n| where ['type'] contains \"microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces\"\r\n| order by id asc\r\n| extend Rank = row_number()\r\n| project id, wsName = tolower(split(id, '/')[8]), selected = iff(Rank == 1, true, false)",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "{workspaceSubscription}"
            ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "timeContext": {
              "durationMs": 86400000
            },
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
          },
          {
            "id": "9dfc0066-580e-4f78-9a2a-37b49862b9a2",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "NSPResourceId",
            "type": 5,
            "description": "NSPs streaming data to selected Log Analytics workspace",
            "isRequired": true,
            "multiSelect": true,
            "quote": "'",
            "delimiter": ",",
            "query": "NTANspRuleRecommendation\r\n| distinct NspResourceId\r\n| project NspResourceId = strcat(\"/subscriptions/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[0], \"/resourceGroups/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[1], \"/providers/Microsoft.Network/networkSecurityPerimeters/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[2])",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "{workspace}"
            ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [
                "value::all"
              ],
              "selectAllValue": "*",
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "timeContext": {
              "durationMs": 0
            },
            "timeContextFromParameter": "timeInterval",
            "defaultValue": "value::all",
            "queryType": 0,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
          },
          {
            "id": "b7534e39-739c-4808-affe-6191dee3ca3b",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "isNSPRRSchemaPresent",
            "type": 1,
            "description": "Schema Check",
            "isRequired": true,
            "query": "let SchemaTable = view () { print isPresent = 'false' };\r\nunion isfuzzy = true SchemaTable, (NTANspRuleRecommendation | take 1 | project isPresent = iff(iscolumnexists('NspResourceId'), 'true', 'false')) \r\n| top 1 by isPresent",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "{workspace}"
            ],
            "isHiddenWhenLocked": true,
            "defaultValue": "value::all",
            "queryType": 0,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
          },
          {
            "id": "fd9e1ff9-a35c-4a95-845d-d8c6ed101a73",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "binningTime",
            "type": 2,
            "isRequired": true,
            "query": "datatable (id:int) [1]\r\n| project value = strcat(max_of({timeInterval:seconds}/3000, 1), 'm'), label = strcat(max_of({timeInterval:seconds}/3000, 1), 'm'), selected = 1",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "{workspace}"
            ],
            "isHiddenWhenLocked": true,
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "timeContext": {
              "durationMs": 1800000
            },
            "queryType": 0,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
          },
          {
            "id": "ca42d128-a33f-4210-9ed5-ac8811aff453",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "NSPResourceNameId",
            "type": 1,
            "query": "let NSPResourceId = dynamic([{NSPResourceId}]);\r\nprint NSPResourceId\r\n| mv-expand id = todynamic(NSPResourceId)\r\n| extend parts = split(id, \"/\")\r\n| extend formatted = strcat(parts[2], \"/\", parts[4], \"/\", parts[-1])\r\n| summarize result = strcat_array(make_list(strcat('\"', formatted, '\"')), \",\")",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "{workspace}"
            ],
            "isHiddenWhenLocked": true,
            "timeContext": {
              "durationMs": 0
            },
            "timeContextFromParameter": "timeInterval",
            "queryType": 0,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
      },
      "name": "MainParameters"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "No NSP Rule Recommendations are currently available in this workspace. If it was recently enabled, please allow 20–30 minutes for recommendation data to become available.",
        "style": "error"
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "isNSPRRSchemaPresent",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "false"
      },
      "name": "no schema error"
    },
    {
      "type": 11,
      "content": {
        "version": "LinkItem/1.0",
        "style": "tabs",
        "links": [
          {
            "id": "976a5362-2282-4c33-9d2b-a10bd9b4b06e",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Rule Recommendations",
            "subTarget": "RR",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "89895267-fa52-45cc-88bb-342688157824",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "NSP Traffic Information",
            "subTarget": "NSP",
            "style": "link"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "isNSPRRSchemaPresent",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "true"
      },
      "name": "links - 9 - Copy"
    },
    {
      "type": 11,
      "content": {
        "version": "LinkItem/1.0",
        "style": "tabs",
        "links": [
          {
            "id": "8f132d2d-465a-49af-ab51-70a3cbd9a84a",
            "cellValue": "Direction",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Inbound Rule Recommendations",
            "subTarget": "Inbound",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "91919ee2-41b4-4cdb-80e3-d4acaea4104b",
            "cellValue": "Direction",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Outbound Rule Recommendations",
            "subTarget": "Outbound",
            "style": "link"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibilities": [
        {
          "parameterName": "Tab",
          "comparison": "isEqualTo",
          "value": "RR"
        },
        {
          "parameterName": "isNSPRRSchemaPresent",
          "comparison": "isEqualTo",
          "value": "true"
        }
      ],
      "name": "InAndOutRR"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "NTANspRuleRecommendation\r\n| where iff('{NSPResourceNameId}' == '\"//*\"', true, (NspResourceId in~ ({NSPResourceNameId})))\r\n| where RuleType == \"ServiceTag\"\r\n    and ResultDirection == \"Inbound\"\r\n    and ResultAction == \"Allowed\"\r\n| extend ParsedIPs = todynamic(SourceIPs)\r\n| mv-expand IP = ParsedIPs\r\n| summarize SourceIPs = make_set(tostring(IP))\r\n    by TrafficType, NspProfile, NspResourceId, RuleType, RuleValue\r\n| extend IPCount = array_length(SourceIPs)\r\n| extend SourceIPs = strcat_array(SourceIPs, \", \")\r\n| project TrafficType,  NspResourceId = strcat(\"/subscriptions/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[0], \"/resourceGroups/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[1], \"/providers/Microsoft.Network/networkSecurityPerimeters/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[2]), NspProfile, RuleType, RuleValue",
              "size": 0,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "[Inbound] ServiceTag Recommendations",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "timeInterval",
              "showRefreshButton": true,
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{workspace}"
              ],
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "RuleValue",
                    "formatter": 1
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "PreviewIPs",
                    "formatter": 1,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "CellDetails",
                      "linkIsContextBlade": true
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "SourceIPs",
                    "formatter": 1,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "CellDetails",
                      "linkIsContextBlade": true
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Url",
                    "formatter": 7,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "Url"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "counterValue",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 10000
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibilities": [
              {
                "parameterName": "Direction",
                "comparison": "isEqualTo",
                "value": "Inbound"
              },
              {
                "parameterName": "Tab",
                "comparison": "isEqualTo",
                "value": "RR"
              }
            ],
            "name": "[Inbound] ServiceTag Recommendations RR"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let Notes = \"Service Endpoint traffic found. Add 'MicrosoftPublicIPSpace' tag or follow Network Identifier TSG to allow the traffic via Service Tag (https://eng.ms/docs/cloud-ai-platform/azure-core/azure-networking/sdn-dbansal/azure-virtual-network-manager/nsp-dataplane-library/articles/ns22tsg/ns22serviceendpoint)\";\r\nNTANspRuleRecommendation\r\n| where iff('{NSPResourceNameId}' == '\"//*\"', true, (NspResourceId in~ ({NSPResourceNameId})))\r\n| where isnotempty(ServiceEndpoints) and ServiceEndpoints!= \"[]\" and ResultDirection == \"Inbound\" and RuleType != \"ServiceEndpoint\" and ResultAction == \"Allowed\"\r\n| extend ParsedIPs = todynamic(ServiceEndpoints)\r\n| mv-expand IP = ParsedIPs\r\n| summarize ServiceEndpoints = make_set(IP) by TrafficType, NspProfile, NspResourceId, RuleType, RuleValue\r\n| extend Count = array_length(ServiceEndpoints), ServiceEndpoints = strcat_array(ServiceEndpoints, \", \")\r\n| project TrafficType,  NspResourceId = strcat(\"/subscriptions/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[0], \"/resourceGroups/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[1], \"/providers/Microsoft.Network/networkSecurityPerimeters/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[2]), NspProfile, RuleType, RuleValue",
              "size": 1,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "[Inbound] Microsoft Traffic - Service Endpoint/SNAT bypass ",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "timeInterval",
              "showRefreshButton": true,
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{workspace}"
              ],
              "visualization": "table",
              "showExpandCollapseGrid": true,
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "ServiceEndpoints",
                    "formatter": 1,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "CellDetails",
                      "linkIsContextBlade": true
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Notes",
                    "formatter": 1,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "CellDetails",
                      "linkIsContextBlade": true
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Url",
                    "formatter": 7,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "Url"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "counterValue",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 10000
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibilities": [
              {
                "parameterName": "Direction",
                "comparison": "isEqualTo",
                "value": "Inbound"
              },
              {
                "parameterName": "Tab",
                "comparison": "isEqualTo",
                "value": "RR"
              }
            ],
            "name": "[Inbound] Microsoft Traffic - Service Endpoint/SNAT bypass "
          },
          {
            "type": 9,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{workspace}"
              ],
              "parameters": [
                {
                  "id": "45e36742-c5b0-45c1-8a60-0ea6d273d5af",
                  "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
                  "name": "ServiceEndpoint_SNAT",
                  "type": 1,
                  "query": "NTANspRuleRecommendation\r\n| where iff('{NSPResourceNameId}' == '\"//*\"', true, (NspResourceId in~ ({NSPResourceNameId})))\r\n| where isnotempty(ServiceEndpoints)\r\n    and ServiceEndpoints != \"[]\"\r\n    and ResultDirection == \"Inbound\"\r\n    and RuleType != \"ServiceEndpoint\"\r\n    and ResultAction == \"Allowed\"\r\n| summarize Count = count()\r\n| project HasServiceEndpointTraffic = Count > 0",
                  "crossComponentResources": [
                    "{workspace}"
                  ],
                  "isHiddenWhenLocked": true,
                  "timeContext": {
                    "durationMs": 86400000
                  },
                  "queryType": 0,
                  "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
                }
              ],
              "style": "pills",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
            },
            "name": "parameters - 4"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "**Above Service Endpoint traffic found**. Add 'MicrosoftPublicIPSpace' tag or follow Network Identifier TSG to allow the traffic via Service Tag (https://eng.ms/docs/cloud-ai-platform/azure-core/azure-networking/sdn-dbansal/azure-virtual-network-manager/nsp-dataplane-library/articles/ns22tsg/ns22serviceendpoint)",
              "style": "info"
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "ServiceEndpoint_SNAT",
              "comparison": "isEqualTo",
              "value": "true"
            },
            "name": "ServiceEndpointText"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "NTANspRuleRecommendation\r\n| where iff('{NSPResourceNameId}' == '\"//*\"', true, (NspResourceId in~ ({NSPResourceNameId})))\r\n| where TrafficType == \"External\" and ResultDirection == \"Inbound\" and ResultAction == \"Allowed\"\r\n| extend ParsedIPs = todynamic(RuleValue)\r\n| mv-expand IP = ParsedIPs\r\n| summarize RuleValue = make_set(tostring(IP)) by TrafficType, NspProfile, NspResourceId, RuleType\r\n| extend Count = array_length(RuleValue), RuleValues = strcat_array(RuleValue, \", \")\r\n| extend SampleIPs = array_slice(RuleValue, 0, 50)\r\n| extend RuleValues = strcat_array(SampleIPs, \", \")\r\n| project TrafficType, NspProfile, NspResourceId = strcat(\"/subscriptions/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[0], \"/resourceGroups/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[1], \"/providers/Microsoft.Network/networkSecurityPerimeters/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[2]), RuleType, RuleValues, RuleValue",
              "size": 0,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "[Inbound] Non-Microsoft rule recommendation",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "timeInterval",
              "showRefreshButton": true,
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{workspace}"
              ],
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "RuleValues",
                    "formatter": 1,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkColumn": "RuleValue",
                      "linkTarget": "CellDetails",
                      "linkIsContextBlade": true
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "RuleValue",
                    "formatter": 5
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "SampleIPs",
                    "formatter": 1,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkColumn": "RuleValues",
                      "linkTarget": "CellDetails",
                      "linkIsContextBlade": true
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Url",
                    "formatter": 7,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "Url"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "counterValue",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 10000
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibilities": [
              {
                "parameterName": "Direction",
                "comparison": "isEqualTo",
                "value": "Inbound"
              },
              {
                "parameterName": "Tab",
                "comparison": "isEqualTo",
                "value": "RR"
              }
            ],
            "name": "[Inbound] Non-Microsoft rule recommendation"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibilities": [
        {
          "parameterName": "Tab",
          "comparison": "isEqualTo",
          "value": "RR"
        },
        {
          "parameterName": "Direction",
          "comparison": "isEqualTo",
          "value": "Inbound"
        },
        {
          "parameterName": "isNSPRRSchemaPresent",
          "comparison": "isEqualTo",
          "value": "true"
        }
      ],
      "name": "Inbound RR"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "NTANspRuleRecommendation\r\n| where iff('{NSPResourceNameId}' == '\"//*\"', true, (NspResourceId in~ ({NSPResourceNameId})))\r\n| where ResultDirection == \"Outbound\" and ResultAction == \"Allowed\"\r\n| extend ParsedValues = todynamic(RuleValue)\r\n| mv-expand RuleValues = ParsedValues\r\n| summarize RuleValues = make_set(RuleValues) by NspProfile, NspResourceId, RuleType\r\n| extend Count = array_length(RuleValues)\r\n| extend RuleValues = strcat_array(RuleValues, \", \")\r\n| extend RuleValuesDisplay =\r\n    iff(strlen(RuleValues) > 50,\r\n        strcat(substring(RuleValues, 0, 50), \"....\"),\r\n        RuleValues)\r\n| project NspResourceId = strcat(\"/subscriptions/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[0], \"/resourceGroups/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[1], \"/providers/Microsoft.Network/networkSecurityPerimeters/\", split(NspResourceId, \"/\")[2]), NspProfile, RuleType, RuleValue = RuleValuesDisplay, RuleValues",
              "size": 1,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "[Outbound] Traffic Recommendations",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "timeInterval",
              "showRefreshButton": true,
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{workspace}"
              ],
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "RuleValue",
                    "formatter": 1,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkColumn": "RuleValues",
                      "linkTarget": "CellDetails",
                      "linkIsContextBlade": true
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "RuleValues",
                    "formatter": 5,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "customColumnWidthSetting": "100ch"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Url",
                    "formatter": 7,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "Url"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "counterValue",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 10000
              }
            },
            "name": "[Outbound] Traffic Recommendations"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibilities": [
        {
          "parameterName": "Direction",
          "comparison": "isEqualTo",
          "value": "Outbound"
        },
        {
          "parameterName": "Tab",
          "comparison": "isEqualTo",
          "value": "RR"
        }
      ],
      "name": "Outbound RR"
    },
    {
      "type": 11,
      "content": {
        "version": "LinkItem/1.0",
        "style": "tabs",
        "links": [
          {
            "id": "11da1eb5-128d-41b2-a87f-0c6872b6fa15",
            "cellValue": "Info",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Allowed Traffic Information",
            "subTarget": "Allowed",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "96416453-8436-4829-afa0-8c7ba74d6923",
            "cellValue": "Info",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Denied Traffic Information",
            "subTarget": "Denied",
            "style": "link"
          }
